            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5800,
            "LocalizeKR": "정말이지, 선생님 때문에\n매번 놀란다고 해야 할까……",
            "LocalizeJP": "ほんと、先生には驚か\nされっぱなしっていうか、",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26005,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600501,
            "DisplayOrder": 260,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7367,
            "LocalizeKR": "휘둘린다고\n해야 할까……",
            "LocalizeJP": "振り回されっぱなしっ\nていうか……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26005,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600501,
            "DisplayOrder": 270,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4200,
            "LocalizeKR": "…응? 뭘 그렇게\n빤히 보는 거야?",
            "LocalizeJP": "……ん？\n何をそんな、\nじっと見てるわけ？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26005,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600501,
            "DisplayOrder": 280,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9633,
            "LocalizeKR": "저기, 설마 또\n이상한 생각 하고 있는 건\n아니겠지?",
            "LocalizeJP": "ねぇ、\nまさかまた変なこと\n考えてないでしょうね？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26005,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600501,
            "DisplayOrder": 290,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4200,
            "LocalizeKR": "난 선생님의\n장난감이 아니라고.",
            "LocalizeJP": "私は先生の\nオモチャじゃ\nないんだから、",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 26005,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2600501,
            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8300,
            "LocalizeKR": "적당히 하지 않으면\n진짜로 화 낼 거야.",
            "LocalizeJP": "いい加減やめないと\n本当に怒るよ。",
